      "content": "it's just not just a \"challenging time\" though. it's every single day. like, i look at the future and i just don't see a version of it where i'm actually happy or at peace. it feels like the world is just designed to make people like me feel like we don't belong. honestly im starting to think it's just a lost cause.",
